N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 34.1 - Definitions

State Regulations

For the purpose of this Part, the following terms shall
have the following meanings: (a) Commissioner means the Commissioner of Agriculture and Markets of the State of

New York. (b) Cheddar cheese, washed curd cheese and colby cheese mean those varieties of cheese as defined
pursuant to sections 17.30, 17.33 and 17.35 of this Title. Notes
